song.title: Analogies 7 (UNP)
song.info:
The first song composed as DigiBoosterPro module for some DiskMag. After it has been rearranged a bit, remastered and added to Analogies LP.
The compilation was planned as composed with pure analogue sounds.
Composed using DigiBoosterPro with use of 16bit sample arrays, then mastered on PC, but never released.
